<br>
Medion. As Nosfy says you've gained too lower level stuns and I suggest you use them.<br>
<br>
Get all 3 set up in lets say spell slots 2 3 &amp; 4. Then create a key like this<br>
<br>
/cast 2<br>
/cast 3<br>
/cast 4<br>
<br>
Name it stun and use it on casting mobs. Works a treat.<br>
<br>
Nothing has changed much other then those 2 spells. Buffs havent changed, or anything and wont affect you till higher levels. Instrument of Nife will come fairly soon and let me tell you how nice this is whilst hunting undead.<br>
<br>
Don't rely on it though. If you can take that undead mob normally you may kill it faster with IoN. If you couldnt solo it before you shouldnt try now.<br>
<br>
Damage tables are the same, however items you'll be wearing will be out of date and items you considered uber will be cheap. If you dont have them already, DW pieces have dropped considerably. As have some of the pally weapons.<br>
<br>
